July 27, 2018
We met right here at the White House to launch a new phase in the relationship between the United States and the European Union.
						President Donald J. Trump					FREER, FAIRER, AND MORE RECIPROCAL TRADE: President Donald J. Trump announced a new phase of transatlantic trade so both sides can win and the world can prosper.FOUR TRADE PRINCIPLES: High-level trade negotiations will follow the 4 principles agreed to by President Trump and President Juncker.NEXT STEPS: President Trump and President Juncker will ensure their closest advisors carry this agenda forward immediately.
